ComicInfo.Summary: "NIGHTINGALE," Part Three With the team decimated, Hanley and Kent pick up the pieces and continue the hunt for Cristina alone. Meanwhile, Cristina, questioning her actions, must escape the trap Hanley sets or remain ensnared in a cycle of murder! Fan favorite Owen Young guest-stars as this issue concludes the third arc of the critically acclaimed comic.
